      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new stand-up set. it's mostly observational stuff about how different cultures and ethnic groups do things differently. i want to lean into some of those relatable, \"we all know someone like this\" vibes. can you help me brainstorm some funny observations or tropes about different groups of people?",
